Single Grid Search for FastKernelSurvivalSVM (Internal)

Source: R/tune.R
tune_fastsvm.Rd

Wrapper for sklearn.model_selection.GridSearchCV.

tune_fastsvm(
  data,
  time_col = "t",
  delta_col = "delta",
  param_grid,
  cv = 5L,
  n_jobs = 1L,
  verbose = 0L,
  refit = TRUE,
  ...
)

Arguments

data

A data.frame with training data.

time_col

Name of the time column.

delta_col

Name of the event column.

param_grid

A list (or list of lists) of parameters to tune.

cv

Integer. Number of folds.

n_jobs

Integer. Use 1 if using custom kernels.

verbose

Integer.

...

Additional fixed parameters (e.g., max_iter).
